<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: chimera assault -->
  <UV_ChimeraAssault.label>嵌合兽袭击</UV_ChimeraAssault.label>
  
  <!-- EN: devourer assault -->
  <UV_DevourerAssault.label>吞噬兽袭击</UV_DevourerAssault.label>
  <!-- EN: Devourer attack -->
  <UV_DevourerAssault.letterLabel>吞噬兽袭击</UV_DevourerAssault.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: A swarm of huge gape-mawed monsters are attacking!\n\nThese creatures' jaws are massive enough to swallow a human whole. Keep your distance! -->
  <UV_DevourerAssault.letterText>一群咧着血盆大口的怪物正在发动袭击！\n\n这些生物的大嘴足以将一整个人生吞掉。离它们远点！</UV_DevourerAssault.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Ghoul attacking -->
  <UV_GhoulSpaceAttack.label>食尸鬼袭击</UV_GhoulSpaceAttack.label>
  <!-- EN: Ghoul attacking -->
  <UV_GhoulSpaceAttack.letterLabel>食尸鬼袭击</UV_GhoulSpaceAttack.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: A vicious humanoid ghoul is attacking!\n\nIt is intent on inhuman savagery and it cannot feel pain. Prepare to defend. -->
  <UV_GhoulSpaceAttack.letterText>一只凶猛的食尸鬼正在发动袭击！\n\n它毫无人性、凶残无比，而且也不惧疼痛。准备迎战！</UV_GhoulSpaceAttack.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: hate chanters -->
  <UV_HateChanters.label>恶咒吟诵者</UV_HateChanters.label>
  
  <!-- EN: nociosphere -->
  <UV_Nociosphere.label>苦痛之球</UV_Nociosphere.label>
  <!-- EN: Nociosphere -->
  <UV_Nociosphere.letterLabel>苦痛之球</UV_Nociosphere.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: A strange metallic sphere has appeared. It hurts to be near it.\n\nYou could attack it, though you're not sure how it might defend itself. Or, you could capture it using a holding platform and learn to make use of its power.\n\nIt seems quiet for now, but it is gaining energy over time. You can suppress the sphere when it is captured to a holding platform, reducing its energy. -->
  <UV_Nociosphere.letterText>一个奇怪的金属球体出现了。光是靠近它就令人浑身发疼。\n\n你大可对其发起攻击，尽管你也不清楚它会怎么保护自己。或者，你可以利用收容平台将其捕获，学习如何利用它的力量。\n\n它表面上还算暂时安分，但实际上它在不断积蓄力量。待你将这个球体捕获至收容平台后，可以通过抑制手段来削弱它的能量。</UV_Nociosphere.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: revenant -->
  <UV_Revenant.label>幽魂</UV_Revenant.label>
  
  <!-- EN: gorehulk assault -->
  <UV_SpaceGorehulkAssault.label>血棘巨人袭击</UV_SpaceGorehulkAssault.label>
  <!-- EN: Gorehulk assault -->
  <UV_SpaceGorehulkAssault.letterLabel>血棘巨人袭击</UV_SpaceGorehulkAssault.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: A group of monstrous, human-like abominations are attacking! Their bodies are ravaged by thick keratin spines which they can launch at a distance. However, their fleshy forms can do little damage at close range. -->
  <UV_SpaceGorehulkAssault.letterText>一群形似人类的丑陋巨怪正在发动袭击！它们身上长有大量锋利的角质脊刺，且能够发射出去。然而只要拉近距离，躯体臃肿笨拙的它们就很难构成威胁了。</UV_SpaceGorehulkAssault.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: obelisk core -->
  <UV_WarpedObelisk.label>方尖碑核心</UV_WarpedObelisk.label>
  <!-- EN: A mysterious obelisk core has crashed into the grav ship and rapidly corrupted the GravEngine.\n\nThe obelisk hums with putrid psychic energy, gradually intensifying as it approaches some dangerous limit. You can send colonists to suppress the obelisk to prevent it from activating.\n\nYou can also mark the obelisk for study to try to learn its purpose and perhaps make use of it.\n\nYou can always attack the obelisk to destroy it, but doing so may unleash unnatural and dangerous phenomena. -->
  <UV_WarpedObelisk.description>一座神秘的方尖碑核心砸入了逆重飞船，并且很快感染了逆重引擎。\n\n这座方尖碑发出带有秽浊心灵能量的嗡鸣声，并且愈发激烈，似乎将要达到某个危险的界限。你可派遣殖民者抑制方尖碑，防止它激活。\n\n你也可将方尖碑标记为调查对象，尝试了解它的意图，或许可以对其加以利用。\n\n你随时可以向方尖碑发起攻击以摧毁它，但这样做可能会招致危险</UV_WarpedObelisk.description>
  <!-- EN: obelisk core -->
  <UV_WarpedObelisk.letterLabel>方尖碑核心</UV_WarpedObelisk.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: A mysterious obelisk has crashed nearby.\n\nThe obelisk hums with putrid psychic energy, gradually intensifying as it approaches some dangerous limit. You can send colonists to suppress the obelisk to prevent it from activating.\n\nYou can also mark the obelisk for study to try to learn its purpose and perhaps make use of it.\n\nYou can always attack the obelisk to destroy it, but doing so may unleash unnatural and dangerous phenomena. -->
  <UV_WarpedObelisk.letterText>一座神秘的方尖碑核心砸入了逆重飞船，并且很快感染了逆重引擎。\n\n这座方尖碑发出带有秽浊心灵能量的嗡鸣声，并且愈发激烈，似乎将要达到某个危险的界限。你可派遣殖民者抑制方尖碑，防止它激活。\n\n你也可将方尖碑标记为调查对象，尝试了解它的意图，或许可以对其加以利用。\n\n你随时可以向方尖碑发起攻击以摧毁它，但这样做可能会招致危险</UV_WarpedObelisk.letterText>
  
</LanguageData>